      "writtenOn": "2018-01-16T17:29:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "i didn\u0027t realize this and Cloud resources have common prefix \"projects/\". I agree that this is confusing.\n\nI\u0027ve replaced \"projects/\" with \"luci-projects/\". Does it address the concern?\n\nContext: the API Design guide seems very sensible to me and I\u0027d like to make it a standard. Currently I am evaluating it with buildbucket api v2 as a guinea pig (see mocks in go/chops-build-api-prd).",
      "parentUuid": "d39fdb22_5658369f",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 67,
        "startChar": 28,
